  "title": "第一卷：地图与领土",
  "image_width": 1536,
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"r7ZTvi-x\">什么是信念，而又是什么让有些信念比其它信念管用？这四个系列解释了贝叶斯概念下的理性，信念，以及证据。本书主题：有些被我们称之为「解释」或「理论」的东西并不总是能像地图一样导航世界。因此，我们心中的地图可能会有和我们工具箱里的其它东西搞混的风险。</p><p data-pid=\"ECrSy8FT\">——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Biases-An-Introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《偏见：序言》</a><sup data-text=\"前言+导读\" data-url=\"https://hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_0/\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup> by Rob Bensinger</p><hr/><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_0/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">前言+导读 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><h2><b>A. 可以预见的错误</b></h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/3102093644\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a9c29fa2f60e21a4dba126aafa937d7_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"4896\" data-image-height=\"3264\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：可以预见的错误</a><h2><b>B. </b>虚假的信念</h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/3102965185\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-473130ab1b21c89cf0609c4cd48b3964_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"5184\" data-image-height=\"3456\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：虚假的信念</a><h2><b>C. 注意到困惑</b></h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/4429031748\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-7915899377bda1786753d202cd49349d_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"3840\" data-image-height=\"2160\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：注意到困惑</a><h2><b>D. 神秘的答案</b></h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/6590373197\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-b122fe4fe3fd8f003c3d2ce286093004_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"5732\" data-image-height=\"3573\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：神秘的答案</a><hr/><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_interlude_1/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">简单的真实 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><hr/><p data-pid=\"zycGiEb0\">上一篇：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//hpmor.xyz/ai2zb_0/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">前言+导读 - 哈利波特与理性之道</a><p data-pid=\"rvorfwK4\">下一篇：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/3102093644\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a9c29fa2f60e21a4dba126aafa937d7_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"4896\" data-image-height=\"3264\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：可以预见的错误</a><hr/><blockquote data-pid=\"Yo8GLyPS\">HPMOR 翻译组译制<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Book-I-Map-And-Territory\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Book I: Map and Territory | Rationality: From AI to Zombies</a></blockquote>",
